description: NYC Office Suites Grand Central Station
overview: NYC Office Suites offers office space with customized, flexible contract terms that accommodate clients regardless of whether they are seeking a single or multiple offices. Each client also receives access to a full range of business services. By offering clients the ability to acquire offices and services in small increments for short periods, or large increments for long periods, NYC Office Suites accommodates business users in a cost efficient manner. NYC Office Suites provides a Class A work environment that would normally be accessible only by large companies. NYC Office Suites also provides economical virtual offices for clients interested in a professional address, mailbox, voicemail and office subscriptions.
